To build you need the following packages (including the *-devel packages)
  * libtorrent (>= 0.12)
  * gtkmm (>= 2.10)
  * libnotify (>= 1.4.2)
  * libcurl (>= 7.14.0)
  * dbus-glib (>= 0.70)
  * gssdp/gupnp (>= 0.1) (Optional)

Then simply run
# ./configure
Or if you check out from svn
# ./autogen.sh
# make
# sudo make install
Or as root
# make install

